{"tid":1473264,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解咁多帶風向post叫勇武抖抖？","createTime":"2019-08-14T19:48:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T18:38:10.000Z","uid":25640,"like":66,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"881d5f43048543714e5ff801e30fc488cd29c12e","tid":1473264,"uid":25640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T19:48:00.000Z","msg":"成日叫勇武抖抖<br />\n勇武都從來無叫你地抖抖啦<br />\n根本就無得抖 打緊戰仲抖抖<br />\n抖咩鬼大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而最主要係</span></span><br />\n依加不斷打<br />\n佢先無時間搜証大搜捕<br />\n勇武派一抖 就比時間佢地做搜捕 捉哂我地返去<br />\n大家唔好再係咁係咁吹風話抖<br />\n一抖勇武比佢有時間搜捕真係玩完"},{"pid":"7ae0a314ecf4db00acb9149344d40f9da0eed80f","tid":1473264,"uid":25640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T19:48:11.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"74beeabffd84e392e2c8c7feecc2aed93cd6036c","tid":1473264,"uid":25640,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T19:48:28.000Z","msg":"屌又準備比人屌我係分化撚一定"},{"pid":"5ddff859af7e27896a47ec9858783ba3a179c89d","tid":1473264,"uid":25640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T19:48:50.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"6e2941b35161e1310c008f9aa0a671df1bc9b842","tid":1473264,"uid":25640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T19:49:11.000Z","msg":"我只係訓唔著出下post"},{"pid":"b19faaa912f19dfbae338a